## 4️⃣ (Bonus) Suggested `requirements.txt`

You can tweak this based on what you actually use, but here’s a solid starting point:

```txt
# Core
numpy
pandas
scikit-learn

# Deep learning (choose one stack; here using PyTorch)
torch
torchvision
torchaudio

# Imaging
Pillow
opencv-python

# Utils
tqdm
pyyaml
matplotlib

# For HTTP requests if fetching tiles
requests
